snippet.title: Vector Strike Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Vector Strike is a fast-paced, physics based, non violent digital sport where mastery and teamwork are key to win. Shoot, double-jump, wall run, slide, dash, pass and score goals in intense 4v4 multiplayer matches where every decision counts.

Wishlist here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2678820/Vector_Strike/
And join us on discord: https://discord.gg/Y9yre7fFt5
